title: Agava
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Southwestern, Tex-Mex, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Farm-to-table cuisine that's Tex-mex inspired but also has other food like flatbread pizza. Vegan suitable dishes include stuffed peppers, tofu tacos, a white bean pizza, kale salad, and a few small side dishes. Reported keeps stock of vegan cheese, so ask for it. The staff know about the ingredients. Has also a gluten free menu.
